%                                         (   0 <=>;   0  =>;   0  <=;   0 <~>)
%            Maximal formula depth :    2 (   2 avg;   8 nst)
%            Number of types       :    2 (   0 usr)
%            Number of type conns  :   10 (  10   >;   0   *;   0   +;   0  <<)
%            Number of symbols     :    7 (   6 usr;   3 con; 0-2 aty)
%            Number of variables   :    4 (   3   ^   1   !;   0   ?;   4   :)
